CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. A11, reads: "Young Pretties - Frog Week went off with a bang, and not the least of the attractions was the number of local lovelies who held the attention of the younger set. Wyetta Turner, Gloria Norwell and Frances Gatewood (left to right) display their charms. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women from left: Wyetta Turner, Gloria Norwell, and Frances Gatewood, posed at bottom of stairs at FROGS week event
